title: 2Cee Essentials Slider Ziplock Bag (50-Pcs), Reusable Freezer Bags Set – Large, Medium, Small Plastic Bags (4.5L, 2.25L & 1L), 50 sticker Labels, bag holder, & Pen – BPA-Free, Food Storage Bag
features: {All-in-One Food Storage Solution}: Organize your kitchen effortlessly with our 50-piece reusable freezer bags set! Includes large freezer bags ziplock (10 pcs, 1 gallon), medium sandwich bags (15 pcs, ½ gallon), and small zip lock bags (25 pcs, 1 quart). Perfect for food storage, meal prep, batch cooking, and keeping your fridge and freezer tidy with reusable, BPA-free zip bags, expandable bottom, durable and leak-proof.

{Complete Kitchen Organizer Kit with Accessories}: Beyond just ziplock bags, this set features bag clips for food storage, 50 freezer label stickers, and a writing pen to easily mark contents and dates. The included ziplock bag holder doubles as a zip lock bag organizer, making this an all-in-one food prep bag solution for busy kitchens. Just the perfect kitchen organiser your kitchen needs!

{Leak-Proof, Expandable Design for Versatile Use}: Our food storage bags feature an anti-leak, expandable bottom design, perfect for upright storage of soups, snacks, and leftovers. Whether you need soup bags for freezer, sandwich bags medium size, or large ziplock bags for batch cooking, these bags are up to the task!

Whether you need soup bags for freezer, sandwich bags medium size, or large ziplock bags for batch cooking, these bags are up to the task!

{Eco-Friendly & Durable Reusable Bags}: Save the planet and your wallet with our freezer bags reusable and designed to last. Made from BPA-free materials, these sealable plastic bags provide a safe, eco-conscious alternative to single-use plastic bags. Ideal for food storage bags, ziplocks, and freezer bags food large size.

{Perfect for Meal Prep & Food Organization}: Keep your freezer and fridge organised with fridge organisers that work for everything from dry erase labels to food prep bags. With writable labels and a convenient ziplock bag holder, this set simplifies meal prep, batch cooking, and everyday storage needs.
